Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.74,0:01:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的假日是从给小鸟喂食开始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.34,0:01:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着是去慢跑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.57,0:01:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可燃垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.20,0:01:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可回收垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.66,0:01:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后回家冲澡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.05,0:01:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平时最后一步是打扫房间和吃早餐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.14,0:01:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是今天...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.98,0:01:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}(小千 绫音来家里玩)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.77,0:01:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小千和绫音来家里玩的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.67,0:01:57.68,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H708EC6&\be10}第17话 休息日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.24,0:02:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是爽子的朋友来玩的日子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.19,0:02:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.13,0:02:09.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸去开门
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.51,0:02:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽子的父亲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.22,0:02:19.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不良少女
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.47,0:02:21.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和爽子一模一...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.46,0:02:24.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没礼貌的家伙 快打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.13,0:02:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.03,0:02:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽子的朋友...吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.11,0:02:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子倒是很有礼貌 就是妆太浓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.00,0:04:14.42,Warning,NTP,0000,0000,0000,banner;28;0;60,本片字幕由异域字幕组制作，仅供试看之用，请于试看后24小时内删除。若因私自散布造成法律问题，本组概不负责。如果喜欢本作品，请购买并支持正版！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.01,0:02:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好 我是爽子的同班同学矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.60,0:02:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底有多少耳洞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.35,0:02:47.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是爽子的朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.26,0:02:48.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千 绫音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.33,0:02:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢 欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.82,0:02:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正在做蛋糕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.53,0:02:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲手做的蛋糕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.20,0:02:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.33,0:02:59.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这个买重了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.17,0:03:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.41,0:03:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咸的东西 要是做点咸的东西就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.78,0:03:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪我考虑不周
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.37,0:03:10.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事 我比较喜欢亲手做的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.07,0:03:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有多少吃多少
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.71,0:03:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃那么多会胖的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.98,0:03:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.13,0:03:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直站在玄关干什么啊 快请进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.36,0:03:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我妈妈 这是我爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.46,0:03:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.82,0:03:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不介意 这个请伯父伯母吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.12,0:21:04.42,Warning,NTP,0000,0000,0000,banner;28;0;60,翻译 瑶瑶 老虎 时间校译 阿 义工 被风早同学萌倒的诺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.50,0:03:31.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 谢谢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.23,0:03:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是矢野绫音和吉田千鹤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.03,0:03:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢你们一直照顾爽子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.68,0:03:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的受了很多照顾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.19,0:03:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们才是 经常麻烦爽子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.93,0:03:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子好不容易才考试及格
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.97,0:03:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌啦 矢野 人家会害羞的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.53,0:04:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 房间倒是出乎意外的充满色彩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.75,0:04:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是自己的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.33,0:04:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想就算和性格不相称也不会给别人添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.42,0:04:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.65,0:04:08.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想的真多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.59,0:04:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么 是相框啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.64,0:04:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我翻了一下郊游的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.10,0:04:23.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于找到了和你们的合照
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.17,0:04:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是灵异照片吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.11,0:04:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好 礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.66,0:04:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是上次庆功会的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.43,0:04:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍的不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.37,0:04:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害 一点也不像灵异照片
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.36,0:04:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 靠的好近
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.91,0:04:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.55,0:04:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再看看后面的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.48,0:05:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么时候给他添了这么大的麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.95,0:05:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是矢野偷拍的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.14,0:05:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错吧 很像一对情侣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.39,0:05:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很重吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.72,0:05:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算他再废 怎么能连女孩子都支撑不住呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.57,0:05:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的真过分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.09,0:05:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那张是不小心被风早发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.95,0:05:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一瞬间...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.55,0:05:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就增加了这么多宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.35,0:05:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能只满足于照片啊 直接去告白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.12,0:05:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对谁?告白什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.55,0:05:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是对风早
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.56,0:05:51.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱的告白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.25,0:05:55.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱着您
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.83,0:05:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.30,0:06:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.75,0:06:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是为了交往啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.14,0:06:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.46,0:06:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明可以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.48,0:06:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.98,0:06:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢 能拥有现状我已经很满足了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.08,0:06:16.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进一步的发展完全无法想像
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.00,0:06:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不早点告白 要是风早被别人抢走了怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.40,0:06:25.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无法做到帮他们加油...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.27,0:06:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也无法祝福他们...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.67,0:06:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 抱歉 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.89,0:06:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.56,0:06:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算喜欢也不一定要马上交往啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.71,0:06:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怜的风早
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.47,0:06:42.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.17,0:06:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是昨天租的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.06,0:06:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.52,0:06:51.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.71,0:06:55.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.31,0:07:02.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.06,0:07:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩德罗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.63,0:07:14.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小丸子很开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.76,0:07:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙很喜欢动物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.48,0:07:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.56,0:07:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.23,0:07:25.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不接吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.57,0:07:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小痞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.65,0:07:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.65,0:07:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 14个未接来电 全是小痞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.99,0:07:37.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不接吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.17,0:07:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 实际上从刚才就在响了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.63,0:07:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太麻烦 所以不接了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.39,0:07:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.08,0:07:54.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚刚都在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.25,0:07:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不能有事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.05,0:08:00.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你立刻把黑沼给我带过来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.37,0:08:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好 马上带过来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.01,0:08:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 我浑身发抖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.35,0:08:13.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我昨晚在租碟店遇到黑沼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.06,0:08:24.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好 老师也想研究些什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.23,0:08:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 研究
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.11,0:08:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,研究
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.87,0:08:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灵异写真
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.85,0:08:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是成人电影吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.75,0:08:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.34,0:08:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社会片 记录片
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.68,0:08:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师果然是大人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.81,0:08:52.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.36,0:08:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盯着我的背后看什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.41,0:08:57.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师说话好像有点鼻音啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.26,0:09:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么一直盯着我看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.71,0:09:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 老师回去以后请把手洗干净 用盐水漱口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.95,0:09:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心点 总是好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.64,0:09:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要那样提醒我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.89,0:09:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那之后我回家就全忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.67,0:09:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.83,0:09:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那啥...只听明白了他借A片的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.51,0:09:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 无论如何 拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.22,0:09:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.67,0:09:41.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 好像很虚弱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.08,0:09:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是求我把黑沼带过去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.23,0:09:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 千鹤说过要去黑沼家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.09,0:09:52.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她想不想见小丸子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.99,0:10:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽子没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.01,0:10:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没做什么坏事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.69,0:10:06.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.81,0:10:08.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋糕有5个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.74,0:10:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始就买了我们的份呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.89,0:10:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真懂事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.59,0:10:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您款待
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.76,0:10:19.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.67,0:10:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 她们开始讲鬼故事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.69,0:10:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我逃出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.59,0:10:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了 放在那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.38,0:10:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯母让我来洗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.26,0:10:30.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个可以用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.68,0:10:33.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很擅长洗东西的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.91,0:10:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 又快又干净
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.01,0:10:37.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.28,0:10:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.32,0:10:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你了 连这些事都帮忙做了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.97,0:10:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 是我想露一手嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.41,0:10:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽子的眉毛 眼睛和鼻子都像伯父
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.48,0:10:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸型和嘴巴就像伯母
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.70,0:10:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真温馨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.96,0:11:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真稀奇 那我上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.86,0:11:06.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风早 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.62,0:11:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是好女孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.47,0:11:12.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.76,0:11:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 去 去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.91,0:11:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 嗯 真恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.73,0:11:27.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确是有点恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.63,0:11:28.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也稍微有点担心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.01,0:11:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小丸子也在...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.23,0:11:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小丸子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.83,0:11:39.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风早同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.58,0:11:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑沼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.54,0:11:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小痞好像身体很虚弱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.02,0:11:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像想和黑沼你商量什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.25,0:11:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想我们一起去小痞家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.62,0:11:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.10,0:12:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 鼻音那么严重漱口水也不管用了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.91,0:12:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.06,0:12:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.15,0:12:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得小丸子也想见你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.52,0:12:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.98,0:12:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样可以么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.29,0:12:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.28,0:12:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不说“我也想见你”
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.54,0:12:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 我觉得翔太可能会说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.42,0:12:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不会说啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.00,0:12:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.58,0:12:43.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还能见到风早
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.64,0:12:53.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.82,0:13:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经...不行了...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.04,0:13:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好脏的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.31,0:13:15.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 我现在的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.94,0:13:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很糟糕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.38,0:13:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先盖上被子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.47,0:13:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.19,0:13:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.14,0:13:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是个感冒嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.96,0:13:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 那个 我也带了很多东西来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.33,0:13:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除灵道具么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.18,0:13:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来敷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.91,0:13:35.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.05,0:13:37.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有请吃这个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.86,0:13:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.21,0:13:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.17,0:13:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后是...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.60,0:13:50.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我要和小痞做像情侣一样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.24,0:13:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可靠...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.60,0:13:57.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 我没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.56,0:14:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个房间没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.65,0:14:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你朝着那里咆哮啊 佩德罗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.95,0:14:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚也是...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.78,0:14:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到有种抓东西的吱吱声
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.14,0:14:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由发烧引发的耳鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.21,0:14:15.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 请放心好好休息
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.07,0:14:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然收拾房间要花点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.49,0:14:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我会打扫干净的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.09,0:14:26.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这方面倒比较在行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.40,0:14:28.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱除邪气么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.90,0:14:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢扫除
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.30,0:14:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 在睡前稍微聊会儿怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.19,0:14:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 什么 说说看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.40,0:14:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就刚刚听到那个 这附近的真实故事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.86,0:14:50.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一个单身男人住的公寓里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.69,0:14:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每晚都有敲门声
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.58,0:14:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开门后 门外却一个人都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.45,0:15:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 在那个公寓的那个房间里...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.45,0:15:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚还被吓得那么惨 他还真能睡得着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.91,0:15:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时候的风早同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.51,0:15:24.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.13,0:15:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擅自的就看了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.36,0:15:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别人的隐私
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.22,0:15:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 不是那样的 是很不好意思啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.88,0:15:35.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这张照片里我在哭嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.78,0:15:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为比赛输了很不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.97,0:15:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后小痞还戏弄我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.27,0:15:44.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想再看一眼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.89,0:15:46.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.87,0:15:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 黑沼你不摸摸小丸子么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.70,0:15:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妨碍它和真田同学不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.28,0:15:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去摸摸看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.86,0:15:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.71,0:15:57.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交往不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.48,0:16:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.09,0:16:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡得真香
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.68,0:16:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.79,0:16:13.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体很轻盈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.97,0:16:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是药起作用了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.21,0:16:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 好像房间的空气不太一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.31,0:16:21.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为收拾过了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.78,0:16:23.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.94,0:16:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再被附身的话就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.92,0:16:30.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 你们还在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.34,0:16:33.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回去快回去 太碍事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.09,0:16:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁还想再来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.87,0:16:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多保重
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.89,0:16:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说算不上谢礼 有什么事就找我商量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.65,0:16:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便说下 翔太和龙的事我什么都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.28,0:16:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想知道他们的弱点的话就来找我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.40,0:16:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没说些什么多余的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.24,0:16:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个翔太啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.45,0:17:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.16,0:17:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 就当作这是谢礼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.36,0:17:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他会高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.65,0:17:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.70,0:17:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 身体变轻盈了真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.30,0:17:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 忘记东西了么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.64,0:17:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽子的蛋糕真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.60,0:17:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 今天也就这样了 下次去玩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.31,0:17:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 来吧 要来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.35,0:18:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得今天一天都在一起 真不舍得分开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.78,0:18:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一起的时间越长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.54,0:18:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就越不想分开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.21,0:18:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我往这边走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.40,0:18:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.62,0:18:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去送她 风早
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.48,0:18:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 这么暗不是很危险么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.06,0:18:27.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会不会 我会注意在回家的路上不吓到别人的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.88,0:18:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我送你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.29,0:18:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我送你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.33,0:18:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.41,0:18:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.62,0:18:36.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不喜欢的话就说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.73,0:18:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是不喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.16,0:18:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔太去的话我也一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.50,0:18:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 你往这走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.98,0:18:52.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩德罗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.52,0:18:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见 晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.03,0:18:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和爸妈问声好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.85,0:18:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.38,0:19:02.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.56,0:19:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.40,0:19:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.36,0:19:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.69,0:19:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白天变短了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.84,0:19:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.93,0:19:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.73,0:19:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为太高兴了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.64,0:19:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想道谢却说不出话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.68,0:19:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不敢看他的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.45,0:20:13.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下 刚才 那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.03,0:20:18.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才荒井老师说如果想答谢的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.23,0:20:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就拉住他 然后闭上眼睛5秒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.01,0:20:22.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.05,0:20:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不管了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.22,0:20:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再这样的话 我就真的不管了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.53,0:20:36.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不管了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.46,0:20:47.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到他这样的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.41,0:20:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和他在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.48,0:20:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着他的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.72,0:20:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.27,0:20:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然变的难舍难分了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.02,0:21:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时别看我这边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.34,0:21:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.45,0:21:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天 想要说出这份感情的日子...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.02,0:21:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也会到来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.73,0:21:25.72,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,その空一杯の紙飛行機　暗いになって
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.73,0:21:25.72,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空中飞满了纸飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.68,0:21:36.04,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いかない　それが答えてなんだって
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.68,0:21:36.04,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要走 那就是回答
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.29,0:21:39.45,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,シャボン玉　飛ばそう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.29,0:21:39.45,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肥皂泡泡 飘飘浮浮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.98,0:21:47.73,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空まではきっと届かない　うちに壊れてる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.98,0:21:47.73,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还未到达天空就破灭消散而去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.09,0:21:53.26,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いま誰知りたいの永遠じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.09,0:21:53.26,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是我们想要的永远
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.52,0:22:00.92,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,このままずっと　いていたいけど
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.52,0:22:00.92,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管想要永远留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.28,0:22:12.19,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,その空一杯の紙飛行機　暗いになって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.28,0:22:12.19,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空中飞满了纸飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.00,0:22:21.73,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ひとつだけ見つけて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.00,0:22:21.73,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只找寻到了属于我的唯一
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.95,0:22:34.87,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(696,364)}千鹤的恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.89,0:22:27.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬日的如期而至
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.01,0:22:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望的脚步声
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.89,0:22:33.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一话 千鹤的恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.15,0:22:42.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这周的2月7日星期天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.15,0:22:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动漫好想告诉你第一次正式活动终于来到了
